2. Why BitcoinSV matters to sovereign states
Not all blockchains are created equal. BSV is unique in its ability to embed true technical sovereignty into economic activity. Hereâ€™s why:

UTXO model: In BSV, every transaction output is unspent until explicitly spent. This creates discrete, auditable units of value that are independently verifiable and traceable. Each transaction is sovereign in itself â€” it cannot be rewritten, censored, or arbitrarily altered.

