Request:

{
  "user_id": "string",          // your internal or micropayment user ID
  "prompt": "string",           // user message
  "context_id": "string|null",  // optional for threaded conversations
  "payment_token": "string",    // signed micropayment receipt in BSV
  "mode": "kintsugi|transform"  // optional processing mode
}
Response:

{
  "response": "string",          // AI output
  "context_id": "string",        // updated for next call
  "usage_units": 1,              // 1 call counted
  "balance_remaining": 9.999     // BSV balance remaining after deduction
}
POST /balance
Check your current prepaid balance.

Request:

{
  "user_id": "string",
  "payment_token": "string"
}
Response:

{
  "balance_bsv": 9.999,
  "total_calls_used": 1,
  "last_call_timestamp": "2026-01-27T12:34:56Z"
}
POST /topup
Add BSV to your account.

Request:

{
  "user_id": "string",
  "micropayment_txid": "string", // verified BSV transaction
  "amount_bsv": 0.1
}
Response:

{
  "success": true,
  "balance_bsv": 10.099
}
3ï¸âƒ£ Usage Accounting Logic
Deduct per call

On /chat, deduct a fixed or dynamic fee (0.001 BSV default).

Log every request

user_id, prompt hash, context_id, timestamp, usage_units, BSV deduction.

Support refunds / disputes

Optional: â€œchargebackâ€ endpoint for accidental calls or failed responses.

Auditable ledger

Each entry immutable â†’ you can reconcile with BSV payments.

4ï¸âƒ£ Security & Fraud Mitigation
Signed payment tokens only â†’ validates micropayment ownership.

Rate limiting per user_id / IP â†’ prevent abuse.

Sandbox execution â†’ AI calls isolated from host environment.

Logging & monitoring â†’ detect repeated failures or suspicious prompts.

5ï¸âƒ£ Optional Enhancements
Tailscale / VPN gating â†’ only allow known IPs for sensitive deployments.

