Usage accounting	Logs each call: user, prompt hash, timestamp, usage units, BSV deduction
Micropayment validation	Verifies BSV payments via Money Button SDK or native chain verification
Rate limiting & throttling	Protects system from abuse
LLM-friendly JSON	Structured input/output suitable for agent integration
Security	API keys not exposed; sandboxed AI execution; optional VPN/Tailscale access
3ï¸âƒ£ Technical Requirements
