This wasnâ€™t explicit in the PRD or blog yet, but it was implicitly hinted in our prior discussions about micropayments and auditable usage. In other words: yes, the idea was â€œin the planâ€ at a conceptual level, but micro-equity/tokenization wasnâ€™t spelled out or baked into the endpoints or accounting model.

Let me clarify how this works and how it changes everything:

1ï¸âƒ£ Tokenized Usage / Micro-Equity Concept
Every app/project is tokenized: Kintsugi, TikTokify, NFT marketplaces, etc.

Every paid interaction mints or distributes a token to the user:

e.g., 1 AI call = 1 micro-token/share in Kintsugi

e.g., 1 NFT listing = 0.1 token in the marketplace project

Tokens represent fractional ownership, not just usage credits

Tokens can be stackable across projects: using multiple apps in the ecosystem accumulates equity across projects

Result: users are no longer just consumers; they become tiny stakeholders in the app ecosystem.

2ï¸âƒ£ Integration with Micropayments
Current API already tracks:

usage_units

balance_remaining

We can extend this to token issuance:

{
  "response": "string",
  "context_id": "string",
  "usage_units": 1,
  "balance_remaining": 9.999,
  "tokens_earned": [
    {"project": "kintsugi", "amount": 0.001}
  ]
}
Each API call mints or credits a micro-equity token in the appâ€™s project

The BSV payment validates the issuance, ensuring one-to-one correspondence between payment and ownership

3ï¸âƒ£ Implications for the Ecosystem
Users become investors by default

Every interaction builds ownership in apps they use

Incentivizes long-term engagement

Apps/projects are self-funding

Usage pays for operations + distributes equity â†’ decentralized investment model

Economic Layer is Unified

Payments â†’ token issuance â†’ auditable on BSV â†’ trackable per user

Can layer Headscale for private enterprise usage, while still tokenizing each API call or interaction

Stackable Ownership

Users can accumulate micro-equity across multiple projects/apps

Encourages users to move across the ecosystem, since every action earns ownership

