Optional Download / Print

iOS: Share API for saving/printing PDFs.

Android: Native print/share API.

PDFs can remain read-only to prevent tampering.

Future-Proofing

Later, can embed PDFs inside tokens themselves (like ordinal-encoded data).

Mobile app interprets token â†’ extracts PDF â†’ verifies hash â†’ displays.

