PRD: BSV Token Wallet + Bit/Sign + Bit/Certificates App
1. Overview / Objective
Build a cross-platform mobile app (iOS + Android) for BSV-based token management, signature capture, and certificate viewing. The app is aimed at founders, investors, and platform users who interact with BSV tokenized shares, staking mechanisms, and blockchain-anchored certificates.

The app integrates with a Next.js backend for business logic, token staking/unstaking, and certificate generation.

2. Key Features
Feature	Description	Notes
Wallet	Hold and manage BSV tokens (e.g., $bWriter)	Fork from Yours Wallet
Token Staking / Unstaking	Users can stake tokens to receive share rights, dividends, and certificate issuance; unstaking removes share rights	Linked to backend & cap table
Bit/Sign (Signature Capture)	Capture handwritten signatures via finger/stylus on mobile	PNG/SVG output, hash anchored on BSV, supports multiple signatures per director/founder
Bit/Certificates (PDF Viewer)	View certificates linked to staked tokens	Verify authenticity via blockchain hash, optional download/print, dashboard integration
Secondary Market Tracking	Display token transfers & certificate ownership history	Backend stores register of members, no dynamic metadata in tokens
KYC Integration	Required for staking & redeeming shares	Minimal: name + email + document upload
Cross-Platform	iOS + Android via React Native	Native SDKs for gestures, touch, PDF viewing
Security	End-to-end encryption for private data & PDFs	TLS, encrypted storage, optional biometrics
