4.2 Bit/Sign Module
Capture signature on touch devices.

Preview and confirm signature.

Generate PNG/SVG (high-res, transparent optional).

Compute SHA-256 hash of PNG/SVG.

Submit hash & encrypted PNG to backend.

Backend anchors hash on BSV.

4.3 Bit/Certificates Module
Display PDFs of staked token certificates.

Verify authenticity:

Fetch PDF.

Verify hash against BSV-anchored record.

Optional download/print.

Show certificate metadata: token ID, owner, stake date.

