Form for user info submission.

Optional document upload (driver license, passport, etc.).

Required to redeem tokens for shares.

API: /api/kyc/submit, /api/kyc/status.

5. Data Models
Entity	Attributes
User	ID, name, email, KYC status, wallet address, token balances
Token	ID (ordinal), series, owner, staked/unstaked, certificate link
Certificate	PDF URL, token ID, hash, issue date, stake info
Signature	PNG/SVG URL, SHA-256 hash, issued by (director/founder), anchored TX ID
Transaction	From, to, amount, timestamp, blockchain confirmation (optional)
