Bitcoin Writer: Own Your Words, Forever

Bitcoin Writer is a word processor that saves your documents directly to the Bitcoin blockchain. Open it, write, save â€” just like any other writing tool. But instead of storing files on your hard drive or in someone elseâ€™s cloud, your work is written immutably on-chain. Permanently. Yours.

