â¸»

Why Blockchain?

The blockchain is an eternal global totem pole: a space where every human has a right to write. From last wills and testaments to creative works, political thoughts, historical accounts, witness statements â€” if it matters, it belongs on-chain.

Unlike traditional platforms, your documents cannot be quietly deleted, altered, or lost. Bitcoin Writer makes this permanence practical: timestamps are immutable, priority and authorship are verifiable, and content is censorship-resistant. Legal documents, contracts, corporate records, intellectual property, and regulatory filings all benefit from this reliability. Your words remain yours â€” forever.

â¸»

How Tokens Work

