Registered token holders may receive dividends from platform revenue. The asymptotic curve ensures early contributors get slightly more tokens per transaction, rewarding risk without inflating rewards. Writersâ€™ activity funds the platform while acquiring stake, investors secure equity, and the system grows sustainably.

