3. Where Dividend Tokens Fit (This Is the Key)
Now we introduce what you called â€œbearer tokens inside securities contractsâ€ â€” which is actually a very strong framing.

Step 1: Bearer Tokens Exist by Default
Every $PATH purchase mints a bearer access token.

Properties:

